metadata.name: EARNFT Genesis Membership NFT
metadata.description: The BLU3CHIP Mobile Genesis Membership NFTs act as an exclusive pass for holders to access future ENFT drops in the EARNFT ecosystem. Additionally, the Genesis Membership NFTs will act as proof of membership for exclusive earning & lifestyle communities that the EARNFT ecosystem partners with in the future.
